## 5. Daily Operations Checklist

Complete the following each business day:

- Review active monitoring alerts.
- Confirm public application availability.
- Confirm API health.
- Review failed authentication anomalies.
- Review failed background jobs.
- Review failed notification deliveries.
- Confirm database backup completion.
- Check database and storage utilization.
- Review elevated error rates.
- Review unresolved customer-impacting tickets.
- Confirm no critical certificate-processing jobs are delayed.
- Record significant findings.

Automated monitoring may perform continuous checks, but an accountable person must review unresolved failures.

